/**
 * Minimal Multicall3-compatible runtime (implements aggregate3, which viem's
 * multicall uses). Fresh Anvil does not predeploy Multicall3, so the
 * integration test injects this at the canonical address via anvil_setCode so
 * the scanner's batched reads work locally.
 */
